ygData.msgSnippet: How are yall s (sorry for the slang, Im from VA and it early here) server s people wise.  Im on Veeshan and it is horrid.  Alot are rude, prices are outragous
ygData.messageBody:
How are yall's (sorry for the slang, Im from VA and it early here) server's people
wise. Im on Veeshan and it is horrid. Alot are rude, prices are outragous (800p
for a FBR). I hate leaving all my loot behind, but if I can find a good server with
good folks I might. Oh, and I still play on Brell, just still a little to crowded
in the newbie areas.

Tiger
